DERBY-961: Error 22001 can include XX-RESOLVE-XX which should be removed
This change is a follow-on to revision 678769, and modifies the string which is used as a message parameter from a hard-coded string to a string fetched from a translatable message file, so that the string "(Binary data value not displayed)" can in the future be translated as appropriate for different Derby locales.
